# 3zip_readme

a) While Login using Air_Route_Finder takes Username and Password if found then we can enter the application else not.

b) When forgot password is clicked the User can send the password to his registered mail but Username and Email should match otherwise error is generated.

c) Using Register an Account user can Register with Username , Password and Email and Thus The password is sent to the mail Specified.

d) Here send_maildef won't work as there a password of registered email should be specified first to log in using that Email and smtp server would change with the change in Email provider.

